descriptions.direction: Located in Ukulhas, Holiday Haven Ukulhas is near the beach. Folhudhoo Harbor and Ukulhas Harbor are local landmarks, and some of the area's activities can be experienced at Nika Island Resort & Spa and Mathiveri Ferry Terminal. Discover the area's water adventures with scuba diving, snorkeling, and windsurfing nearby, or enjoy the great outdoors with hiking/biking trails.
descriptions.general: Holiday Haven Ukulhas in Ukulhas provides accommodations with a garden and a shared lounge. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and a shared kitchen, along with free Wifi throughout the property. The accommodation provides full-day security, a concierge service, and currency exchange for guests. At the guest house, all units include air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a kitchen, a dining area, a safety deposit box, and a private bathroom with a walk-in shower, bathrobes, and slippers. An oven, a toaster, and fridge are also featured, as well as a coffee machine and a kettle. At the guest house, units come with bed linen and towels. As an added convenience, the guest house offers packed lunches for guests to bring on excursions and other trips off-property. The area is popular for snorkeling and cycling, and bike rental is available at this 3-star guest house. The guest house has a picnic area where you can spend the day outdoors. Ukulhas Beach is a 1-minute walk from Holiday Haven Ukulhas.
